PageV02P043
# @COMMENT: A similar passage is found in WZATB on HSNXV01P474D. This refers to the migration of ʿUmar b. al-Khaṭṭāb and ʿAyyāsh b. Abī Rabīʿah, and refers to a "longer account" about efforts of Abū̄ Jamīl b. Hishām and his brother al-Ḥārith to disuade ʿAyyāsh. In WZATB, the account is longer and refers to Abū̄ Jahl not Abū̄ Jamīl. WYBWS has a much longer account more similar to WZATB. @EC_12/31/22@

