PageV02P043
# @COMMENT: This fragment is a small part of a similar passage found in WZATB on HSNXV01P479F that recounts where the migrants from Mecca originally lived upon their arrive in Madīnah, this referring to where ʿUthmān b. ʿAffān stayed. Oddly, this fragment is not otherwise extant in the corpus. @EC_02/10/23@

