# @COMMENT: HBHXV37P464A indicates that the dispute in which Sahl b. Saʿd was involed dealt with the location of the first masjid. This seems to refer to HSNXV01P494C and story of the those who invited Muḥammad to settle with different clans in Madīnah. One of those was the Banī Sāʿidah, of which Sahl was a member. It appears that Ibn Isḥāq is stating that Sahl was only of those involved in the dispute. 

