PageV01P385
# @COMMENT: Portions of this fragment appear in WZATB on HSNXV01P606B, in reference to the change of the qiblah to HSNXV01P606D referring to the Battle of Badr, although the phrasing is different, and WZATB does not include dates in the section. No analogous fragments are found elsewhere in the corpus. @EC_01/27/23@

