# @COMMENT: Passage is not found in the redaction of Ibn Hishām but would logically follow the passage found on HSNXV01P646A to p. 647A. It recounts the freeing al-ʿAbbās after his capture Badr. For a similar passage see WSFAB, WHAYA, WAIYA, and WMSAH. @EC_12/16/22@

