# @COMMENT: WZATB includes a similar story in HSNXV2P294D to p. 295A in the story of the Raid on the Banū al-Muṣṭaliq and the Prophet's marriage to Jūwayrīyah bint al-Ḥārith in a narrative structure much like that found in WSFAB, WYBWS, WMSAH, WSSAA, WAMAQ, and WJHZA. WMSAH also witnessed an account completely unlike his other version and unlike other versions. The story related by WSACD is narratively different and more similar to that found in WAIYA. WZAZA also relates the story with yet another narrative structure. WBSAB produced a truncated version. WAKMW witnessed a tradition that lists Jūwayrīyah bint al-Ḥārith as an eyewitness not found in other witnesses. @EC_12/12/22@

