# @COMMENT: See comment on TDSHV12P037A for an statement from Ḥanash about what appears to be a different battle or protion of this battle not mention in the redaction of Ibn Hishām. For similar accounts. see via the witness of Yūnus b. al-Bukayr, THRXV02P298A; via the witness of Aḥmad b. Khālid al-Wahbī, see BGHXV02P378A, NYMXV02P1065A, TLBXV06P2983A; via the witness of Abū Muʿawīyah Yazīd b. Zurayʿ, NYMXV02P1065A; via the witness of ʿAbd Allāh b. Mubārak, see NYMXV02P1065A; via the witness of Zuḥayr b. Muʿawīyah, NYMXV02P1065A; also see WZAZA, and for versions of this passage from Ibn Isḥāq without a wintess, see NYMXV02P1064A (a truncated version), KTHSV03P364A.

