# @HBHXV28P563A_END_WSACD 
VAR_HBHXV28P563B VAR_KTHQV06P206A حدثنا @TR2_YISI@ يعقوب قال حدثنا @TR1_SACD@ أبي عن ابن اسحاق قال حدثني يزيد بن أبي حبيب المصري عن عبد الرحمن بن شماسة التجيبي قال سمعت عقبة بن عامر الجهني يقول وهو على منبر مصر سمعت رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم يقول لا يحل لامرئ يبيع على بيع أخيه حتى يذره. @HBHXV28P563A_END_WSACD
PageV28P563
# @ COMMENT: HBHXV28P563A is a variation on HSNXV02P331A and p. 332A as is a variation on HBHXV28P207A and HBHXV28P209A. It is clear from the isnād statement on HSNXV02P331A that the context is the same as that stated in HBHXV28P563A. The speaker, ʿAqabah b. ʿĀmir al-Juhanī, participated in the Battle of Ṣiffīn (TKXXV04P256A) at which he is purported to have killed ʿAmmār b. Yāsir (TKXXV03P196A). He participated in the conquest of Egypt and was appointed over the Egyptian army under Muʿawīyah in 47 (SJTXV01P246A). His involvment at Ṣiffīn would explain why he goes unnamed in the WZATB copy. MDRXV03P1661A via copy of Yazīd b. Zurayʿ; WKKHV01P160A via copy of WABAB. 

