# @COMMENT: In KTHRV05P152A the transmitter is listed as Abū Isḥāq. It appears this is a mistake. The transmitter to Abū Isḥāq is Yazīd b. ʿAbd Allāh b. Qusayṭ, who was one of Ibn Isḥāq's informants. This is likely to be Ibn Isḥāq. 

