# @TDSHV24P175A_BEG_WSACD أخبرتنا أم البهاء فاطمة بنت محمد بن أحمد قالت أنا أبو طاهر بن محمود أنا أبو بكر بن المقرئ أنا أبو الطيب محمد بن جعفر نا عبيد الله بن سعد بن إبراهيم نا @TR2_YISI@ عمي عن @TR1_SACD@ أبيه عن أبي اسحاق قال وقتل صفوان بن المعطل السلمي شهيدا في سنة تسع عشرة في أرمينية
@TDSHV24P175A_END_WSACD 
PageV24P175
# @COMMENT: According to TBRCV04P053A, THKXV02P357A, TDSHV47P278A based on the witness of Salamah b. al-Faḍl, Ibn Isḥāq places Safwan's death in the year 19 during the conquest of al-Jazīrah. In these texts, Ibn Isḥāq includes an expanded account of the conquest, correspondence between ʿUmar and Saʿd b. Abī Waqqas, as well as the circumstances of Safwan's death. Also see KTHBV07P076A, KTHBV07P096A, and KHDMV02P547A that quote Ibn Isḥāq without a witness. For an Ibn Isḥāq passage witnessed by Salamah b. al-Faḍl that places Safwan's death in the conquest of Armenia, see RZJXV04P42A, BRSXV02P725A, TDSHV24P175B. For references to Ibn Isḥāq's account of Safwan's death in Armenia without witness, see THRXV03P031A

# @TDSHV24P161A_BEG_WSACD
