### |||||| ترجمة عمير مولى عبد الله بن عباس

# @BKHBV06P532A_BEG_WSACD
VAR_BKHBV06P532A VAR_ZTTHV02P202A VAR_RZJXV06P380B قال علي عن @TR2_YISI@ يعقوب بن إبراهيم عن @TR1_SACD@ أبيه عن ابن إسحاق وكان ثقة مولى عبد الله بن عباس رضي الله عنهما @BKHBV06P532A_END_WSACD
PageV06P532
# @COMMENT: This passage is not found in the redaction of Ibn Hishām nor is ʿUmayr. al-Dhahabī states that ʿUmayr was the mawlā of Umm al-Faḍl bint al-Ḥārith, although others asserted that he was the mawlā of ʿAbd Allāh b. ʿAbbās. He was supposed to have only related stories from ʿAbd Allāh b. ʿAbbās, Usāmah b. Zayd, Abū Juhaym, and Umm al-Faḍl bint al-Ḥārith (DHTIV07P209A). Ibn Manjuwayh states that he was the mawlā of Umm al-Faḍl bint al-Ḥārith and that he died in Madīnah in 104/722 (MRSXV02P088D). This is a standard identity clarification usually inserted following the first entry for a person or after some important event involving that person. Placement based on the above collection of traditions is the only reference to ʿUmayr in the corpus. @EC_02/05/23@

