# @COMMENT: The isnad after Ibn Isḥāq is حدثنا أحمد بن محمد البغدادي حدثنا عبيد الله بن سعد حدثنا عمي حدثني أبي عن. This passage is not found in the redaction of Ibn Hishām. Passage deals with Ṣadaqah. Might also be placed in biography of al-Ḥasan b. ʿAlī.

