# @COMMENT: the hadith that follow use the isnad from Ibn Isḥāq as follows: حدثنا أحمد بن محمد البغدادي حدثنا عبد الله بن سعد حدثنا عمي حدثنا أبي عن. This passage is not found in the redaction of Ibn Hishām. Passage refers to the sighting of the moon to mark the ending of fasting. 

