# @COMMENT: This passage is not found in the redaction of Ibn Hishām. Deals with punishments for stealing. Similar passages are also found in WABAB, WMSAH, and WAKMW, which places the value at ten dirhāms (also see YNQXV23P279C witnessed by WSACD). Passage provisionally placed in fiqh section under ḥadd punishments. @EC_01/10/23@

