# @COMMENT: Surāqah b. Kaʿb b. ʿAbd al-ʿUzzā b. al-Ghazīyah b. ʿAmr is mentioned in WZATB on HSNXV01P702A as a participant at Badr. He is not mentioned elsewhere. It appears the comment is fragmented in mid sentince in the middle of a critique of someone's opinion of the identity of Surāqah. 

